"Desa la teva escena i torna-ho a provar."

#: editor/scene/3d/lightmap_gi_editor_plugin.cpp
msgid ""
"No meshes with lightmapping support to bake. Make sure they contain UV2 data "
"and their Global Illumination property is set to Static."
msgstr ""
"Sense malles amb suport de lightmapping per coure. Assegureu-vos que "
"continguin dades UV2 i que la seva propietat d'Il·luminació global estigui "
"establerta en Estàtica."

#: editor/scene/3d/lightmap_gi_editor_plugin.cpp
msgid ""
"To import a scene with lightmapping support, set Meshes > Light Baking to "
"Static Lightmaps in the Import dock."
msgstr ""
"Per importar una escena amb suport de lightmapping, configureu Meshes > "
"Light Baking a Static Lightmaps al moll d'importació."

#: editor/scene/3d/lightmap_gi_editor_plugin.cpp
msgid ""
"To enable lightmapping support on a primitive mesh, edit the PrimitiveMesh "
"resource in the inspector and check Add UV2."
msgstr ""
"Per habilitar el suport de lightmapping en una malla primitiva, editeu el "
"recurs PrimitiveMesh a l'inspector i marqueu Afegeix UV2."

#: editor/scene/3d/lightmap_gi_editor_plugin.cpp
msgid ""
"To enable lightmapping support on a CSG mesh, select the root CSG node and "
"choose CSG > Bake Mesh Instance at the top of the 3D editor viewport.\n"
"Select the generated MeshInstance3D node and choose Mesh > Unwrap UV2 for "
"Lightmap/AO at the top of the 3D editor viewport."
msgstr ""
"Per habilitar el suport de lightmapping en una malla CSG, seleccioneu el "
"node CSG arrel i trieu CSG > Bake Mesh Instance a la part superior de la "
"finestra de visualització de l'editor 3D.\n"
