msgstr "Depuració del canal UV"

#: editor/scene/3d/mesh_instance_3d_editor_plugin.cpp
msgid "Create NavigationMesh"
msgstr "Crea NavigationMesh"

#: editor/scene/3d/mesh_instance_3d_editor_plugin.cpp
msgid ""
"Before converting a rendering mesh to a navigation mesh, please verify:\n"
"\n"
"- The mesh is two-dimensional.\n"
"- The mesh has no surface overlap.\n"
"- The mesh has no self-intersection.\n"
"- The mesh surfaces have indices.\n"
"\n"
"If the mesh does not fulfill these requirements, the pathfinding will be "
"broken."
msgstr ""
"Abans de convertir una malla de renderització en una malla de navegació, "
"verifiqueu:\n"
"\n"
"- La malla és bidimensional.\n"
"- La malla no té superposició superficial.\n"
"- La malla no té autointersecció.\n"
"- Les superfícies de malla tenen índexs.\n"
"\n"
"Si la malla no compleix aquests requisits, el camí es trencarà."

